  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.3.1\" data-text=\"Version 2.3.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.3.1</h3>\n<p>February 5, 2020</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.work:work-*:2.3.1</code> is released.  <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/cdec0090b957bd9020ff2462c3006cbb1381ddc6..d7ffb1e3214adc08092397ca92881b05fb69521a/work\">Version 2.3.1 contains these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Better manage the lifecycle of <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">Notification</code>s for long running <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">Worker</code>s that run when a foreground <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">Service</code> is active. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/1218539\">aosp/1218539</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/147249312\">b/147249312</a>)</li>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">WorkManager</code> now depends on <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.sqlite:sqlite-framework:2.1.0</code> stable. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/1217729\">aosp/1217729</a>)</li>\n<li>Added lint rules to ensure that a <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">foregroundServiceType</code> is specified in the <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">AndroidManifest.xml</code> when using <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">foregroundServiceType</code>s in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ForegroundInfo</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/1214207\">aosp/1214207</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/147873061\">b/147873061</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_230_3\" data-text=\"Version 2.3.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.3.0</h2>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/cdec0090b957bd9020ff2462c3006cbb1381ddc6..d7ffb1e3214adc08092397ca92881b05fb69521a/work"
}